{"tid":1157454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港交所傳研熔斷機制","createTime":"2019-05-16T09:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T15:48:54.000Z","uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"eb8df6224fbcac5fb049a0d0cdb5d2fb31c5f015","tid":1157454,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:59:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/2137849/港交所傳研熔斷機制\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F2137849%2F%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80%E5%82%B3%E7%A0%94%E7%86%94%E6%96%B7%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%B6&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdfwzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=c056c03e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/2137849/港交所傳研熔斷機制</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEF00zh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEF00zh.jpg&h=fce415e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據本地傳媒報道，港交所(00388)據稱正初步向業界諮詢「熔斷機制」(Circuit Breaker)意見，在本港出現重大市場危機時，恒生指數若下挫某個百分比，是否有需要暫停現貨及期貨等市場交易，以免淪為「大鱷提款機」。<br />\n<br />\n港交所發言人回應傳媒查詢時表示，已初步接觸市場，討論有關提升市場微結構的各項措施，希望令香港市場更具競爭力，提高整體市場流動性。提升市場微結構措施是港交所在2019至2021戰略規劃中提出的重點工作，但發言人拒絕評論是否初步探討「熔斷機制」的可行性。<br />\n<br />\n現時港交所只對恒指及國指成分股實施市場波動調節機制，若相關成分股於5分鐘內，價格上漲或下跌10%，便要進入5分鐘「冷靜期」。內地曾於2016年1月推出熔斷機制，惟實施初期便多次因市場大幅波動而觸發機制，短短數日便遭叫停。"},{"pid":"968b757a598f67d04df1255e36f6927cb679e73a","tid":1157454,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:01:21.000Z","msg":"跌10%<br />\n斷<br />\n開返 再跌10%<br />\n又斷<br />\n<br />\n想托都冇得托<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a679a9e2e23e6a7f36108e1200145113b24586e9","tid":1157454,"uid":63154,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:04:49.000Z","msg":"成日都想鎖死啲資金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港經歷過咁多次股災都冇穿冇爛，停市往往更加恐慌"},{"pid":"7cbc343d0489757303ed0ee27d2a49fa0eef7b42","tid":1157454,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:05:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0497ba670b0b00e76aa911bbfe2c69ab201fe995","tid":1157454,"uid":41524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:06:29.000Z","msg":"接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n終於玩完喇"},{"pid":"bccabfd3775380128dc667079ded5cd61609f2f5","tid":1157454,"uid":18251,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:08:01.000Z","msg":"咩叫自由市場"},{"pid":"169e6f3eedbfe2e159b7487b2976f8bcf992f5c5","tid":1157454,"uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:11:51.000Z","msg":"痴撚線, cash out都唔撚俾"},{"pid":"ad58af90435690e43061ac6d08ef4654fc4ec6b1","tid":1157454,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:14:18.000Z","msg":"香港天線"},{"pid":"fe27002a221cacd788010859980dc3cf2c5736d6","tid":1157454,"uid":232060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:15:20.000Z","msg":"其實美國都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a359432764ca2f3e4b954f7e11ca8e5c824b34a2","tid":1157454,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:16:09.000Z","msg":"遲早有埋外匯管制"},{"pid":"835dfc3b6ddbf540f38e7fd00617f8db2aad2bed","tid":1157454,"uid":73598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe27002a221cacd788010859980dc3cf2c5736d6","tid":1157454,"uid":232060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:15:20.000Z","msg":"其實美國都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T13:09:58.000Z","msg":"人地平民都有票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb9e7109b521ec5f88de44c418f347efbdfc03c","tid":1157454,"uid":66242,"lik